title: Skinny Puppy - Weapon 2013
description:
Skinny Puppy is a Canadian electronic music group, formed in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada in 1982. The group is widely considered to be one of the founders of the electro-industrial genre. Weapon is the twelfth studio album by the band. (wikipedia)
